The paper focuses on designing a new probabilistic data structure for efficient storage and query processing of multivariate data, which is a common problem in database systems (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS). The proposed structure is also relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) applications, which often involve processing large amounts of data and require efficient batch lookup operations.
